  "body": "**BUG REPORT**: During the create workflow, Portworx native driver has the PVC namespace information. But this isn't getting passed to the Portworx Create API. As a result, the Portworx service side handler doesn't get the namespace information.\r\n\r\nIt will also be helpful to send PVC annotations in the Create API call.\r\n\r\n/kind bug\r\n\r\n**What happened**:\r\nPortworx native driver didn't send PVC namespace to the Portworx Create API\r\n\r\n**What you expected to happen**:\r\nPortworx native driver should send the PVC namespace to the Portworx Create API\r\n\r\n",
